metadata.name: Spirit Town #1
metadata.description: Spirit Town is a collection of 2,000 Haunted Manors, each with its own mystical spirits to contend with. Each Manor (and its spirits) are created using Procedural Generation (Proc-Gen). This project was created to exemplify new and improved ways of generating unique artwork through the use of advanced scripts and protocols. Spirit Town Holders will be entitled to 1 Free Airdrop per/NFT owned. (January 20, 2023)
